creator: NTUC Enterprise
descriptionHtml:
FairPrice brings you nationwide-best deals and exclusive discounts as the online grocery you can always rely on. Shop for a wide range of your household needs – fresh fruits and vegetables, meat and seafood, eggs, milk, beers, wine, coffee, baby products and even toiletries! Have them delivered to your doorstep at convenient 2-hour timeslots.

With thousands of products, you can find your favourite brands like Milo, Huggies, Tiger Beer, Carlsberg, Friso, Oreo, Coca-Cola, Tesco, Marigold, Nestle, Haagen Dazs and more!

Savings on savings!
* Frequent exclusive online deals equal greater savings when you shop on the app
* Look forward to Weekly 3-Day Must Buy and Purchase with Purchase specials
* Get notified every time we have a special deal – just for you!
* Save time by paying in-app and having your items delivered to your doorstep

Smooth shopping experience
* Clean, user-friendly interface brings you a pleasant shopping experience
* Create shopping lists and simply check them out the next time you shop
* Search for the products you need with a comprehensive search function
* Choose from 2-hour Home Delivery timeslots

Secure online transactions
* Secure payments via your preferred card
* Worry-free transactions assured with secured payment gateways

Curated tips for your benefit
* Whip up our recommended recipes or read up on the best ways to save money, improve your lifestyle or provide better options for your family.

Shop for a wide range of your household needs – fresh fruits and vegetables, meat and seafood, eggs, milk, beers, wine, coffee, baby products and even toiletries! Have them delivered to your doorstep at convenient 2-hour timeslots.

With thousands of products, you can find your favourite brands like Milo, Huggies, Tiger Beer, Carlsberg, Friso, Oreo, Coca-Cola, Tesco, Marigold, Nestle, Haagen Dazs and more!

Savings on savings!
* Frequent exclusive online deals equal greater savings when you shop on the app
* Look forward to Weekly 3-Day Must Buy and Purchase with Purchase specials
* Get notified every time we have a special deal – just for you!
* Save time by paying in-app and having your items delivered to your doorstep

Smooth shopping experience
* Clean, user-friendly interface brings you a pleasant shopping experience
* Create shopping lists and simply check them out the next time you shop
* Search for the products you need with a comprehensive search function
* Choose from 2-hour Home Delivery timeslots

Secure online transactions
* Secure payments via your preferred card
* Worry-free transactions assured with secured payment gateways

Curated tips for your benefit
* Whip up our recommended recipes or read up on the best ways to save money, improve your lifestyle or provide better options for your family.

descriptionShort: With FairPrice Online, shopping at FairPrice is now easier, anytime, anywhere
title: FairPrice: Fast, Reliable

creator: NTUC Enterprise
descriptionHtml:
FairPrice brings you nationwide best deals and exclusive discounts as Singapore’s most trusted grocery retailer. Experience a brand new digital and retail shopping experience with all your grocery needs in one place!

Shop online & in stores
Enjoy a unique experience within one app for all your grocery needs. Fast and easy grocery shopping both online and in stores!

Speedy home deliveries
No time to hit up the supermarket? Click away and enjoy deliveries in as fast as 2 hours!

Earn & redeem LinkPoints
Get ready for easier rewards with LinkPoints. Offset your online and in-store purchases with LinkPoints, without your physical Plus! Card!

With the FairPrice app you can:
- Earn and redeem LinkPoints easily (with no minimum spend)
- Go cardless & pay digitally in stores
- Digitally track your purchases and keep yourself on track

Pay in stores, in app
Pay for in-store purchases digitally through the FairPrice app. Earn and redeem LinkPoints and track your savings on the go.

descriptionHtml:

Shop online & in stores

Speedy home deliveries

Earn & redeem Linkpoints
Get ready for easier rewards with Linkpoints. Offset your online and in-store purchases with Linkpoints.

Link Rewards
Enjoy fabulous deals at other Link partners. Link Rewards provides easier ways to earn and redeem Linkpoints.

Pay in stores, in app

Shop safer & faster in grocery stores
Scan & Go is a scan-and-pack, in-app initiative that allows you to maintain safe distances in stores and skip long queues!

Deals & promotions
Grocery shopping on a budget? Browse weekly deals, bestsellers and personalised recommendations for everyday low prices.

Search & browse in store
Be efficient and save time when grocery shopping! Check the availability of items in stores near you before your grocery trip.

Smart shopping lists
Tips for simple and efficient grocery shopping:
Check product availability in your nearest store on the app before making your way down.
Build your shopping list with ongoing store promotions so you don't miss a thing!

Wide variety of products

Easy, delicious recipes

creator: NTUC Enterprise
descriptionHtml:
With the FairPrice app, your grocery and dining needs are integrated in an innovative platform at your fingertips. Get access to the best deals and exclusive discounts brought to you by Singapore’s leading retailer and cooked food provider.

You can:
- Enjoy faster and easier shopping and dining experiences
- Get rewards on all your purchases
- Access exclusive promotions and more!

YOUR ONE APP FOR ONLINE & IN-STORE GROCERIES, DINING PRIVILEGES AND MORE!

From grocery shopping online and in-store to ordering your favourite meal at Kopitiam, you can do it all with the FairPrice app. Explore a wide variety of quality products from local and global brands, and satisfy your cravings with joyful food experiences.

Order or pay at Kopitiam*
Get double joy: Save 10% and earn Linkpoints on your meals at Kopitiam when you order and pay via the app.
*Available at selected outlets and coming soon to more!

Get cooking inspiration
Serve up delicious meals with our library of recipes for every occasion, using products you can find online and in FairPrice stores.

Speedy grocery delivery
No time to hit the supermarket? Click away and have your groceries delivered in as fast as 2 hours!

Pay in-store, via the app
Go cardless in stores! Make your purchases digitally through the FairPrice app. Earn and redeem Linkpoints and track your savings on the go.

Earn & redeem Linkpoints
Get ready for easier rewards with Linkpoints. Offset your online and in-store purchases with Linkpoints, without your physical Link card!

Link Rewards
Enjoy exclusive deals at other Link partners. Link Rewards provides easier ways to earn and redeem Linkpoints.

Skip the queue
Experience easy, breezy checkouts with Scan & Go, our in-app scan-and-pack feature.

Deals & promotions
Grocery shopping on a budget? Browse weekly deals, bestsellers and personalised recommendations at everyday low prices.

Search & browse in-store
Be efficient and save time when grocery shopping! Check the availability of items in stores near you before your grocery trip. Create a smart shopping list to keep you on track when you’re shopping, so you don’t miss a thing!
